high_descs: move dining table to the left of the stove
pick up a spoon from the table
move to the stove to the right
put the spoon on a pan on the stove
pick up the pan with spoon from the stove
move to the table behind you
put the pan on the table.

high_descs: go to the black table to your left
pick up the spoon that is on the edge of the table
take the spoon to the stove that is to the right of the black table
put the spoon in the bowl that is on the left back burner
pick up the spoon and the bowl
carry the spoon and bowl back to the black table
place the spoon and bowl on the table where the spoon was sitting before

Pick up the spoon at the edge of the table.
Bring the spoon over to the stove.
Put the spoon on the frying pan that's on the left back burner.
Pick up the frying pan with the spoon on it.
Bring the frying pan over to the black table.
Put the frying pan with the spoon on the table to the left of the potted plant and behind the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with a spoon on it on the table.
